<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Contact us</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Css/HeadFoot.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Css/style-contact.css">
  <script src="/Home page/header.js" defer></script>
</head>

<body>
  <div id="header">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
  </div>

  <section class="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Contact us</h1>
      <p>The Velora team is delighted to assist you with your order,
        we understand the importance of being readily available to our clients,
        especially when it comes to our exquisite 18k gold jewelry.
        Your satisfaction is our top priority,
        and we're here to assist you every step of the way.
        Please select your preferred method of contact below.</p>

      <div class="contact-content">
        <img src="/Images/contact us/image1.png" alt="Luxora Jewelry Showcase" class="contact-img">
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h2>Customer Service</h2>
          <p>Our dedicated customer service team is available every day except Friday,
            from 11:00 AM to 7:00 PM.</p>
          <p>You can reach us through our: <br><br>
            Phone number: +(20)123456789 <br>
            Email: Velora@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-content">
        <div class="contact-text">
          <h2>Office Location</h2>
          <p>Our office is located in Egypt, Cairo.<br>
            Please note that our office is restricted to employees or business<br> affairs only.</p>
            <p>Visit our jewelry boutique located inside Garden 8 Mall, New Cairo.</p>

          <h2>Business Hours</h2>
          <p>Monday - Thursday: 11:00 AM - 7:00 PM <br><br>
            Saturday - Sunday: 11:00 AM - 7:00 PM <br><br>
            Friday: Closed</p>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-map">
          <p>Find Us on the Map</p>
          <iframe
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3453.606616190225!2d31.48603187542654!3d30.04737701907496!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x14583d3a973d7dff%3A0x94d4388411b6356e!2sGarden%208%20Mall!5e0!3m2!1sen!2seg!4v1718282890875!5m2!1sen!2seg"
            width="100%" height="300" style="border:0; border-radius: 10px;"
            allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
          </iframe>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Separated form section, centered -->
  <div class="containerr">
    <form action="/contact-us" method="POST">
      <div class="row">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name">
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email *" required>
      </div>
      <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone number">
      <textarea name="comment" placeholder="Comment" rows="4"></textarea>
      <br>
      <button type="submit">Send</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
